        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "_integrationTestNotes": "Integration tests should verify: (1) Activity_ReimburseExpenses (plain bpmn:task, auto-executes in Zeebe) calls real payment/reimbursement system — in integration: replace with real job worker; (2) Activity_NotifyRejection (plain bpmn:task, auto-executes) sends real rejection notification email — in integration: replace with real job worker; (3) Activity_1l5wj0t (plain bpmn:task, auto-executes) performs pre-reimbursement setup — in integration: replace with real job worker. Note: "
}
